{
  "texts": [
    "The scores are then rounded to the closest integers, and only scores greater than or equal to 3 are kept.",
    "There are 3 categories of coarse-grained quality levels.",
    "• Fine-Grained Quality Score (QS-fine): Similar to QS-coarse, we take the raw score (provided as score) from the regressor instead of the rounded one.",
    "The score is presented as ⌊score * 10⌋.",
    "Thus, it is at least 10 times finer than QS-coarse."
  ]
}